# ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress

!syntax description /Materials/ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress

## Overview

!! Replace these lines with information regarding the ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress object.

## Example Input File Syntax

!! Describe and include an example of how to use the ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress object.

!syntax parameters /Materials/ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress

!syntax inputs /Materials/ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress

!syntax children /Materials/ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress

Computes an eigenstrain from an initial stress

Input Parameters

  • eigenstrain_nameMaterial property name for the eigenstrain tensor computed by this model. IMPORTANT: The name of this property must also be provided to the strain calculator.

    C++ Type:std::string

    Options:

    Description:Material property name for the eigenstrain tensor computed by this model. IMPORTANT: The name of this property must also be provided to the strain calculator.

Required Parameters

  • base_nameThe base_name for the elasticity tensor that will be used to compute strain from stress. Do not provide any base_name if your elasticity tensor does not use one.

    C++ Type:std::string

    Options:

    Description:The base_name for the elasticity tensor that will be used to compute strain from stress. Do not provide any base_name if your elasticity tensor does not use one.

  • blockThe list of block ids (SubdomainID) that this object will be applied

    C++ Type:std::vector

    Options:

    Description:The list of block ids (SubdomainID) that this object will be applied

  • boundaryThe list of boundary IDs from the mesh where this boundary condition applies

    C++ Type:std::vector

    Options:

    Description:The list of boundary IDs from the mesh where this boundary condition applies

  • computeTrueWhen false, MOOSE will not call compute methods on this material. The user must call computeProperties() after retrieving the MaterialBase via MaterialBasePropertyInterface::getMaterialBase(). Non-computed MaterialBases are not sorted for dependencies.

    Default:True

    C++ Type:bool

    Options:

    Description:When false, MOOSE will not call compute methods on this material. The user must call computeProperties() after retrieving the MaterialBase via MaterialBasePropertyInterface::getMaterialBase(). Non-computed MaterialBases are not sorted for dependencies.

  • constant_onNONEWhen ELEMENT, MOOSE will only call computeQpProperties() for the 0th quadrature point, and then copy that value to the other qps.When SUBDOMAIN, MOOSE will only call computeSubdomainProperties() for the 0th quadrature point, and then copy that value to the other qps. Evaluations on element qps will be skipped

    Default:NONE

    C++ Type:MooseEnum

    Options:NONE ELEMENT SUBDOMAIN

    Description:When ELEMENT, MOOSE will only call computeQpProperties() for the 0th quadrature point, and then copy that value to the other qps.When SUBDOMAIN, MOOSE will only call computeSubdomainProperties() for the 0th quadrature point, and then copy that value to the other qps. Evaluations on element qps will be skipped

  • initial_stress_xxinitial stress xx compoent

    C++ Type:std::vector

    Options:

    Description:initial stress xx compoent

    Options:

    Default:False

    C++ Type:bool

    Options:

    Description:Whether or not this object should use the displaced mesh for computation. Note that in the case this is true but no displacements are provided in the Mesh block the undisplaced mesh will still be used.

examples/mud_2D_qualitative/sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_c/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_c.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_c.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]

examples/mud_2D_qualitative/sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_d/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_d.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_d.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_3D/L_5.5/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = '../gold/psic_L_5.5_rho_0_sample_1.txt'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = '../gold/Gc_L_5.5_rho_0_sample_1.txt'
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./disp_z]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./solid_z]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_z
    component = 2
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./x_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
  [./y_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
  [./z_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_z
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    initial_stress_zz = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]

  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_ksp_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      preonly       ilu          200         200                0                    '
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -ksp_grmres_restart -sub_ksp_type -sub_pc_type -pc_asm_overlap'
  # petsc_options_value = 'asm      31                  preonly       ilu          2'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -mat_mffd_err -pc_factor_shift_type -pc_factor_shift_amount'
  # petsc_options_value = 'ilu      1e-5          NONZERO               1e-15'
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_0.5/run6/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '7.943282E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '7.943282E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 2.083333E+00
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.055164E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.055164E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 7.943282E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial

examples/mud_2D/exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_1_sample_1/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_1_sample_1.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_1_sample_1.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

[GlobalParams]

  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]

[Functions]

    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_5.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]

    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_5.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'

    variable = 'disp_x'

  [../]

    multi_app = fracture

    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = disp_x

    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]

      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]

    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_10/run10/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '1.995262E+01 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '1.995262E+01 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]

    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.812010E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]

    type = GenericConstantMaterial

  [../]

    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 1.995262E-01
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04

    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'

  [../]
[]

    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]

    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'

    direction = to_multiapp

    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]

    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = disp_x

  [../]
  [./react_y]

    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]

    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_10/run9/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'

    block = 'film'
  [../]

    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_5/run12/fracture.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./d]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./nonnegtivity]
    type = BoundsAux
    variable = bounds_dummy
    bounded_variable = d
    upper = 1
    lower = 0
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./damage]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolution

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_5/run1/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

  [../]

  [../]

  [../]

    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]

    component = 1
  [../]

    value = 0

      secondary = 'right'

    [../]

  [../]

    block = 'film'
  [../]

    youngs_modulus = 2.083333E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]

    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]

    block = 'film'

examples/mud_2D/exp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_4/mechanical.i

  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

[GlobalParams]

[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]

    value = 0

      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '1.000000E+01 0 0'
    [../]

    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'

    block = 'film'
  [../]

    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 1.000000E-01
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 1.000000E-01
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]

examples/mud_2D/exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_10/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_10.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_10.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

  [../]

    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]

    variable = disp_z
    component = 2
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]

    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
  [./y_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]

    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_z
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]

  [../]

    eigenstrain_names = is

  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]

  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
[]

  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_ksp_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      preonly       ilu          200         200                0                    '
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -ksp_grmres_restart -sub_ksp_type -sub_pc_type -pc_asm_overlap'
  # petsc_options_value = 'asm      31                  preonly       ilu          2'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -mat_mffd_err -pc_factor_shift_type -pc_factor_shift_amount'
  # petsc_options_value = 'ilu      1e-5          NONZERO               1e-15'
  dt = 1e-4

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

  [../]

  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]

    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 8.333333E+02
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]

    d = d
  [../]

    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.162278E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.162278E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]

[Functions]

    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_5.txt
  [../]

    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_5.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]

    family = SCALAR
  [../]

    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]

    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]

    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]

    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]

      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2

    block = 'film'
  [../]

examples/mud_2D/sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_1_sample_2/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_1_sample_2.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_1_sample_2.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_2D/exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0.5_sample_9/mechanical.i

[Functions]

  [../]

    data_file = ../gold/psic_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0.5_sample_9.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

[GlobalParams]

    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'

    variable = 'd_ref'

    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]

    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer

  [../]

      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.162278E+01 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.162278E+01 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]

    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 2.083333E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.503124E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]

  [../]

    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]

    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]

    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./solid_z]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_z
    component = 2
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]

    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
  [./y_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
  [./z_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_z
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
[]

  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    initial_stress_zz = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]

  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
[]

  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'

  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_ksp_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      preonly       ilu          200         200                0                    '
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -ksp_grmres_restart -sub_ksp_type -sub_pc_type -pc_asm_overlap'
  # petsc_options_value = 'asm      31                  preonly       ilu          2'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -mat_mffd_err -pc_factor_shift_type -pc_factor_shift_amount'
  # petsc_options_value = 'ilu      1e-5          NONZERO               1e-15'
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true

  print_linear_residuals = false

    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
